reviewText: It a very great fantastic story and has a great meaning to it.
Love it! For an Indi Film this is a great story line. It has some major issues that are going on right now behind closed doors.  Also, it is my story, so I should love it. Thanks for the support

A true and powerful story.  I personally know the writer and subject of the Movie.

The hair on my arms stood up and tears ran down my cheeks.  It is really about the true power of Love.

I really enjoyed this movie and my only wish was that it lasted longer so the viewer could find out more about how the people were doing after the tragedy. Based on true life story of a dear friend, this movie was awesome to watch and can't wait to see more films from her!
